<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>رزين النَّيْسَابُورِي.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> سُفْيَان بن حُسَيْن , وَغَيره.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>كناه الْحُسَيْن بن مَنْصُور.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>١٧٩٩ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو حَفْص:</span> عمر بن عبد الْعَزِيز بن<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>عمرَان بن أَيُّوب بن مِقْلَاص.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
